Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.29,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊司令官 哥歇爾上將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:09.13,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Planet "Masjid"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.78,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,44 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.29,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Christoph von K{\fnArial}ö{\r}fenhiller (at28)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.30,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zieten
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.51,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hauser von Steiermark
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.29,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kosel
